Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.67,0:00:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奧布軍會在克列塔島再次與Minerva發生衝突
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.14,0:00:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捕捉到艦影
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.22,0:00:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距離60 11點鐘方向
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.31,0:00:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全員準備起錨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.15,0:00:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重複 全員準備起錨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.07,0:00:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下令紅色狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.65,0:00:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下令紅色狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.40,0:00:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,駕駛員到搭乘機內待命
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.24,0:00:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,炮手 蜂式彈齊射
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.33,0:00:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,炮擊來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.00,0:00:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.26,0:00:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.59,0:00:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉克絲也說了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.60,0:00:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先下決心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.18,0:00:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再去行動
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.60,0:00:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是想成就某事時的唯一途徑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.94,0:00:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.02,0:00:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.27,0:01:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以你非去不可 不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.71,0:01:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡嘉莉·尤拉·阿斯哈 Strike rouge出動
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.22,0:01:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基拉·大和 Freedom出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.23,0:03:12.65,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,Tristan Isolde發射
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.31,0:03:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,9點鐘方向發現奧布艦群繼續接近
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.57,0:03:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿瑟 準備對艦導彈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.90,0:03:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓雷和露娜去牽制
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.82,0:03:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.58,0:03:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打算在克列塔海域前後夾擊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.75,0:03:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不妙 就算轉向也會被另一方逼入死路
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.26,0:03:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無路可退 只有突破一途了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.68,0:04:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哼 今天來綠色的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.11,0:04:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.03,0:04:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.95,0:04:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢伙果然也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.71,0:04:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這老面孔都快看膩了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.88,0:04:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天一定要擊落你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.01,0:05:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我們不想讓奧布受到襲擊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.02,0:05:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 沒睡醒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.03,0:05:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你想和哪邊打?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.87,0:05:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別逃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.21,0:05:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想開點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.87,0:05:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不然 會死哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.63,0:05:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不想攻擊 別逼我攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.97,0:05:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.75,0:05:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海神號 導彈發射口中彈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.42,0:05:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,倉光號 上前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.67,0:06:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目標路線轉向240
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.67,0:06:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 讓第二戰鬥群再向前逼近一點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.59,0:06:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我圍過去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.84,0:06:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minerva的武器還在 不能魯莽出動
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.85,0:06:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Murasame隊在幹什麼 怎麼還不趕快幹掉…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.52,0:06:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,實戰和您平常玩的遊戲不同
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.60,0:06:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒那麼簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.53,0:06:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別管他們的M.S. 交給地球軍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.12,0:06:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們負責Minerva
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.95,0:06:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬場上尉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.12,0:06:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要擊沉那個 就全都結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.62,0:06:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.79,0:06:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,右舷後方 上空出現Murasame 12
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.71,0:06:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別讓他們纏上 打下來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.63,0:06:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.90,0:07:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minerva
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.32,0:07:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別想再囂張下去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.76,0:07:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都叫你別逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.93,0:07:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saviour lmpulse 呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.01,0:07:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要由我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.52,0:07:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和Chaos Abyss交戰中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.86,0:07:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哼 小意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.53,0:07:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上 這次一定要成功
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.11,0:07:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.45,0:08:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.87,0:08:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左滿舵 引擎最大功率
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.57,0:08:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Freedom
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.73,0:08:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.90,0:08:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奧布軍 立即停戰撤軍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.08,0:08:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奧布不能參加這種戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.08,0:08:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢伙又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.25,0:08:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣保護不了任何東西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.01,0:08:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別任憑地球軍擺佈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.34,0:08:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快想起奧布的理念
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.51,0:08:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,失去理念 軍隊還為何存在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.26,0:09:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.10,0:09:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總是只會...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.86,0:09:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說這種漂亮話!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.28,0:09:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.70,0:09:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.54,0:09:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也給我..適可而止吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.31,0:09:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手 基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.56,0:09:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.81,0:09:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說了別再做這種事 回奧布去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.41,0:10:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然搞不清楚你們在搞什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.91,0:10:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然每次都來搗亂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.74,0:10:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在發什麼呆 尤拉·羅馬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.66,0:10:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的話都忘了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.92,0:10:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩艦都給我打沉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.33,0:10:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戶高上校
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.00,0:10:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們…沒有指揮權
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.30,0:10:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知…知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.59,0:10:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打Minerva 叫你快打Minerva
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.93,0:10:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們只要擊沉那個就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.52,0:10:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,退下 基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.18,0:10:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的力量只是讓戰場更混亂而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.11,0:10:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.78,0:10:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們是我的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.88,0:10:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.55,0:10:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦…艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.80,0:11:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖沒有明確與我們敵對
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.97,0:11:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但上次本艦由於那艘船的介入
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.89,0:11:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蒙受了巨大的損失
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.81,0:11:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作為敵艦對待
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.48,0:11:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.98,0:11:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.07,0:11:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手 基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.15,0:11:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在看哪裏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.92,0:11:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.29,0:11:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奧盧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.44,0:12:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chaos歸艦 醫療班到第八閘門前待機
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.20,0:12:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,救援兵準備出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.45,0:12:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Abyss的遇難地點在坐標1018 beta
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.37,0:12:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minerva Force Silhouette
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.04,0:12:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.38,0:12:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Force Silhouette 射出
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.24,0:12:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,氘核光束 照射
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.87,0:12:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奧布全軍攻擊Minerva
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.45,0:12:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重複 奧布全軍攻擊Minerva
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.05,0:13:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小隊各機 跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.39,0:13:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.56,0:13:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.06,0:13:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡嘉莉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.74,0:13:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奧布有何理由攻擊那艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.91,0:13:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是我們的敵人就不能攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.16,0:13:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奧布不能攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.33,0:13:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡嘉莉小姐 果然是她
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.75,0:13:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.17,0:13:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.25,0:13:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.26,0:13:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是現在我們的國家的領導者尤拉·羅馬·賽蘭的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.34,0:13:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那這就是國家的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.10,0:13:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我們作為奧布軍人就有責任遵守
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.10,0:13:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.35,0:13:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論這條道路充滿多少艱難險阻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.44,0:13:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們都必須堅持
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.77,0:13:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.13,0:14:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.30,0:14:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請退下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.71,0:14:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自從離開國土
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.30,0:14:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們就已經做好了在此戰死的覺悟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.47,0:14:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.39,0:14:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不讓開的話就恕我付諸武力了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.23,0:14:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡嘉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.57,0:14:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡嘉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.99,0:14:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們的淚水與氣魄
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.91,0:14:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好看著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.08,0:14:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.42,0:14:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.17,0:14:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.01,0:15:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,露娜瑪莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.09,0:15:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.01,0:15:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.36,0:15:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.30,0:15:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,引擎最大功率 左舵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.64,0:15:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主炮和右舷彈射器中彈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.73,0:15:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發生火災
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.15,0:16:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趕快進行滅火
