Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.24,0:16:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,露娜瑪莉雅機重度破損 進行收容
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.24,0:16:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還剩最後一口氣 打下它
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.91,0:16:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對 我們就該這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.00,0:16:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要打下Minerva
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.59,0:16:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minerva Sword Silhouette
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.67,0:16:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要把他們戰艦全劈了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.34,0:16:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.78,0:16:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.62,0:16:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先打過來的是地球軍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.95,0:16:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們想讓Minerva被擊沉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.53,0:16:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.03,0:16:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以叫你回去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.95,0:17:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然說不想打那又為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.12,0:17:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 本艦也上前
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.70,0:17:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,引擎最大功率
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.71,0:17:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.71,0:17:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,引擎最大功率
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.04,0:17:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,引擎最大功率
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.54,0:17:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.79,0:17:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是要打下Minerva吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.21,0:17:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就非去不可
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.81,0:17:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.23,0:17:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡嘉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.74,0:17:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡嘉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.99,0:17:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.99,0:17:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然明白…雖然也明白你說的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.75,0:17:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 卡嘉莉現在在哭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.92,0:18:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為不願意看到變成這樣所以在哭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.18,0:18:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.02,0:18:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要說這場戰鬥 這些犧牲都是迫不得已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.77,0:18:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全都是奧布和卡嘉莉的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.27,0:18:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣你就能攻擊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.78,0:18:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對著卡嘉莉正要保護的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.53,0:18:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.28,0:18:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我就要攻擊你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.31,0:18:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.64,0:18:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saviour它...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.90,0:18:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奧布軍航母接近中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.32,0:19:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,12點鐘方向 距離2000
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.82,0:19:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,導彈來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.07,0:19:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迴避 迎擊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.24,0:19:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,航母來前面想幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.59,0:19:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手 別這樣Takemikazuchi
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.52,0:19:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼 戶高
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.36,0:19:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.36,0:19:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尤拉大人請去避難
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.94,0:19:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全員棄艦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.78,0:19:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.95,0:19:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全員棄艦 重複 全員棄艦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.45,0:19:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takemikazuchi 別這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.46,0:20:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡嘉莉小姐 請退下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.22,0:20:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡嘉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.80,0:20:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會遵守擊沉Minerva的命令直到最後
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.89,0:20:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,失去艦船和將士的責任全由我承擔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.40,0:20:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來奧布的勇猛也能傳遍世界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.33,0:20:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,送總司令官走
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.16,0:20:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們也全部下艦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.08,0:20:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.67,0:20:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是為了尤拉·羅馬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.67,0:20:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是為了國家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.76,0:20:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請允許我留下來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.76,0:20:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.84,0:20:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恕難從命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.43,0:20:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.68,0:20:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到目前為止的責任由我承擔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.19,0:21:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還有未來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.49,0:21:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.52,0:21:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然死的覺悟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.69,0:21:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就帶著志同道合的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.69,0:21:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到Archangel去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.12,0:21:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣總有一天會找到道路
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.87,0:21:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戶高上校
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.45,0:21:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.87,0:21:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算是為了我和今天枉死在這裏的將士
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.79,0:21:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快走
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.68,0:23:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為何 這是重複過無數次的言語
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.68,0:23:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為何 即使如此詢問也沒有任何回應
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.68,0:23:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 現在蠢動的這個生命是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.20,0:24:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同伴們悲傷的幻影向狄蘭達爾述說著什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.97,0:24:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下集 機動戰士Gundam Seed Destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.58,0:24:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,FATES
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.50,0:24:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向新的世界飛去 GUNDAM
